iginally%20slated%20for%20Phase%202%2C%20has%20been%20rescheduled%20for%20Phase%203%20due%20to%20the%20death%20of%20the%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20(BSP)%20candidate.%20All%2026%20constituencies%20of%20Gujarat%20will%20cast%20their%20votes%20in%20a%20single%20phase%2C%20along%20with%20two%20constituencies%20in%20Goa.%20The%20remaining%2014%20constituencies%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20predominantly%20situated%20in%20north%20Karnataka%2C%20are%20also%20scheduled%20for%20polling%20on%20the%20same%20day%2C%20marking%20the%20conclusion%20of%20voting%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAhead%20of%20the%20polls%2C%20here%20is%20a%20look%20at%20some%20of%20the%20key%20battles%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EGandhinagar%3A%20Amit%20Shah%20vs%20Sonal%20Patel%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGujarat's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgandhinagar-lok-sabha-constituency-a-bjp-stronghold-with-notable-leaders-5175061%5C%22%3EGandhinagar%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0Lok%20Sabha%20constituency%20is%20a%20key%20stronghold%20for%20the%20BJP.%20Since%201989%2C%20it%20has%20consistently%20delivered%20victories%20to%20the%20party%2C%20spanning%20six%20terms%20for%20BJP%20veteran%20Lal%20Krishna%20Advani%20and%2C%20and%20most%20recently%20in%202019%2C%20for%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20who%20secured%20a%20comprehensive%20win%20by%20over%205%20lakh%20votes.%20As%20the%20elections%20approach%20this%20year%2C%20the%20Home%20Minister%20faces%20Congress%20candidate%20Sonal%20Patel%2C%20aiming%20to%20maintain%20the%20constituency's%20allegiance%20to%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMainpuri%3A%20Dimple%20Yadav%20vs%20Jaiveer%20Singh%20vs%20Shiv%20Prasad%20Yadav%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incumbent%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-2024-mainpuri-mulayam-singhs-stronghold-samajwadi-party-dominant-since-1996-5269981%5C%22%3EMainpuri%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0MP%2C%20Dimple%20Yadav%2C%20faces%20a%20formidable%20opponent%20in%20Jaiveer%20Singh%20of%20the%20BJP.%20While%20initially%20perceived%20as%20a%20head-to-head%20battle%2C%20the%20entry%20of%20Shiv%20Prasad%20Yadav%20from%20the%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20(BSP)%20has%20presented%20a%20third%20contender.%20Dimple%20Yadav%2C%20who%20clinched%20Mainpuri%20in%20a%20bypoll%20following%20the%20death%20of%20Mulayam%20Singh%20Yadav%20in%202022%2C%20secured%20victory%20with%20a%20surge%20of%20sympathy%20votes.%20This%20upcoming%20election%20poses%20as%20the%20primary%20litmus%20test%20for%20her.%20In%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20the%20contest%20was%20confined%20to%20the%20BJP%20and%20SP%2C%20with%20Mulayam%20Singh%20Yadav%20emerging%20victorious%20against%20BJP's%20Prem%20Singh%20Shakya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBaramati%3A%20Supriya%20Sule%20vs%20Sunetra%20Pawar%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Maharashtra's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbaramati-lok-sabha-election-family-feud-in-baramati-potential-supriya-sule-sunetra-pawar-battle-5307631%5C%22%3EBaramati%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20all%20eyes%20are%20fixed%20on%20the%20Pawar%20family%20rift%20as%20the%20stage%20is%20being%20readied%20for%20a%20clash%20between%20Supriya%20Sule%2C%20representing%20the%20Sharad%20Pawar%20faction%20of%20NCP%2C%20and%20her%20cousin%20Ajit%20Pawar's%20wife%20Sunetra%20Pawar%2C%20the%20NCP%20candidate.%20Since%202009%2C%20Supriya%20Sule%2C%20Sharad%20Pawar's%20daughter%20and%20the%20incumbent%20MP%2C%20has%20consistently%20won%20in%20this%20constituency.%20Baramati%20has%20long%20been%20a%20stronghold%20of%20the%20Sharad%20Pawar-led%20NCP%2C%20dating%20back%20to%20his%20tenure%20as%20an%20MLA%20in%201967.%20Throughout%20subsequent%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20candidates%20backed%20by%20him%20have%20emerged%20victorious%20in%20Baramati%2C%20including%20Ajit%20in%201991.%20Sharad%20Pawar%20himself%20held%20the%20parliamentary%20seat%20from%201996%20until%20Supriya%20succeeded%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EShivamogga%3A%20BY%20Raghavendra%20vs%20Geetha%20Shivarajkumar%20vs%20KS%20Eshwarappa%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-2024-shimoga-ex-chief-ministers-children-bjp-rebel-to-battle-for-this-karnataka-seat-5595861%5C%22%3EShivamogga%3C%2Fa%3E%20Lok%20Sabha%20constituency%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20KS%20Eshwarappa%2C%20the%20suspended%20BJP%20leader%20has%20announced%20his%20intention%20to%20run%20as%20an%20independent%20candidate%2C%20challenging%20the%20incumbent%20MP%2C%20BY%20Raghavendra%2C%20son%20of%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20BS%20Yediyurappa%2C%20and%20Geetha%20Shivrajkumar%2C%20the%20Congress%20candidate%2C%20spouse%20of%20Kannada%20superstar%20Shiva%20Rajkumar%20and%20daughter%20of%20another%20Karnataka%20Chief%20Minister%20Sarekoppa%20Bangarappa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20parliamentary%20area%2C%20consisting%20of%20eight%20assembly%20segments%2C%20has%20been%20firmly%20under%20the%20control%20of%20the%20Yediyurappa%20family%20since%202009.%20In%20the%202009%20general%20elections%2C%20BY%20Raghavendra%20secured%20victory%20with%20a%20margin%20of%20over%204.82%20lakh%20votes%20and%20a%20vote%20share%20of%2050.58%20per%20cent.%20In%202014%2C%20he%20relinquished%20the%20seat%20to%20his%20father%2C%20BS%20Yediyurappa%2C%20who%20triumphed%20with%20a%20commanding%20lead%20of%20over%206%20lakh%20votes%20and%20a%2053.69%20per%20cent%20vote%20share.%20Returning%20to%20Raghavendra%20in%202019%2C%20he%20secured%20a%20landslide%20victory%20with%20over%207.29%20lakh%20votes%20and%20a%20vote%20share%20of%2056.86%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBerhampore%3A%20Yusuf%20Pathan%20vs%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBerhampore%20in%20West%20Bengal%20has%20long%20been%20a%20stronghold%20for%20the%20Congress%20party.%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury%2C%20the%20current%20MP%2C%20has%20held%20this%20position%20since%201999.%20In%20both%20the%202019%20and%202014%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20Mr%20Chowdhury%20secured%20victory%20over%20candidates%20from%20Trinamool%20Congress%20(TMC)%20by%20considerable%20margins.%20As%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20approach%2C%20Berhampore%20is%20in%20for%20a%20contest%20between%20Mr%20Chowdhury%2C%20Nirmal%20Kumar%20Saha%20of%20the%20BJP%20and%20ex-cricketer%20Yusuf%20Pathan%20of%20the%20TMC.%20%C2%A0Mr%20Chowdhury%20has%20represented%20the%20Congress%20party%20in%20Berhampore%20for%20three%20consecutive%20terms%20from%202009%20to%202019.%20The%20Congress%20veteran%20also%20triumphed%20in%20the%202016%20Assembly%20elections%20across%20all%20seven%20Assembly%20segments%20falling%20within%20the%20constituency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EVidisha%3A%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%20vs%20Bhanu%20Pratap%20Sharma%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Madhya%20Pradesh's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-2024-vidisha-congress-brings-in-old-guns-to-counter-mamas-magic-5592232%5C%22%3EVidisha%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%C2%A0it%20will%20be%20a%20contest%20between%20Mama%20and%20Dada.%20Since%201967%2C%20the%20Jana%20Sangh%20has%20predominantly%20held%20the%20Vidisha%20Lok%20Sabha%20constituency%20and%20subsequently%20the%20BJP%2C%20with%20only%20two%20exceptions%20in%201980%20and%201984%20when%20the%20Congress%20candidate%2C%20Pratap%20Bhanu%20Sharma%2C%20secured%20the%20seat.%20From%201989%20onwards%2C%20BJP%20representatives%20have%20consistently%20won%20the%20Vidisha%20seat.%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%2C%20who%20served%20five%20terms%20from%201991%20to%202004%2C%20is%20now%20making%20a%20comeback%20after%20nearly%20two%20decades%20to%20vie%20for%20the%20seat.%20He%20faces%20Mr%20Sharma%2C%20the%20sole%20Congress%20victor%20in%20this%20constituency's%20history.%20Mr%20Chouhan's%20rapport%20with%20voters%20affectionately%20referred%20to%20as%20%26quot%3BMamaji%2C%26quot%3B%20ha