rgil%20have%20already%20raised%20a%20banner%20of%20revolt%20against%20the%20party%20over%20the%20choice%20of%20the%20candidate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rebel%20leaders%20of%20the%20NC%20and%20the%20Congress%20have%20fielded%20a%20candidate%20backed%20by%20all%20the%20religious%20and%20social%20groups%20of%20Kargil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBehind%20the%20controversy%20is%20an%20old%20political%20rivalry%20between%20Muslim-majority%20Kargil%20and%20Buddhist-majority%20Leh%20districts%20of%20Ladakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20Congress%20declared%20Tsering%20Namgyal%20as%20its%20official%20candidate%2C%20Congress%20and%20NC%20leaders%20in%20Kargil%20opposed%20the%20move%20and%20declared%20Haji%20Haneefa%20Jan%20as%20their%20candidate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Jan%20is%20the%20district%20president%20of%20the%20National%20Conference%20in%20Kargil%20and%20was%20chosen%20as%20a%20consensus%20candidate%20by%20the%20local%20leadership%20of%20both%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20NC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIslamia%20School%20and%20the%20Khumaini%20Trust%20-%20the%20two%20powerful%20socio-religious%20institutions%20of%20Kargil%20-%20backed%20Mr%20Jan%20and%20ensured%20no%20other%20candidate%20from%20Kargil%20was%20contesting%20to%20avoid%20a%20split%20of%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELadakh%20will%20vote%20on%20May%2020%20to%20elect%20the%20lone%20MP%20from%20the%20Union%20Territory.%20These%20are%20the%20first%20elections%20in%20Ladakh%20since%20the%20abrogation%20of%20Article%20370%20split%20the%20erstwhile%20state%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20into%20two%20Union%20Territories%20-%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20and%20Ladakh.%20Votes%20will%20be%20counted%20on%20June%204.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715016240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-11%2Fq1ejctio_national-conference_625x300_29_November_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmass-resignation-hits-national-conference-over-india-bloc-ladakh-pick-5603745%22%2C%22su