20staff%20member%20attached%20to%20the%20Peace%20Room%20in%20the%20Raj%20Bhavan%2C%20had%20approached%20the%20police%20post%20inside%20the%20Governor's%20House%20and%20accused%20Mr%20Bose%20of%20molesting%20her.%20Mr%20Bose's%20office%20later%20issued%20a%20statement%20denying%20the%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20refuse%20to%20be%20cowed%20down%20by%20engineered%20narratives.%20If%20anybody%20wants%20some%20election%20benefits%20by%20maligning%20me%2C%20God%20Bless%20them.%20But%20they%20cannot%20stop%20my%20fight%20against%20corruption%20and%20violence%20in%20Bengal%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715011980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fq8hac6s_cv-ananda-bose_625x300_06_May_24.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-didigiri-bengal-governors-message-for-mamata-banerjee-5603072%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bengal%20Governor%20CV%20Ananda%20Bose%20issued%20a%20warning%20of%20sorts%20for%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%2C%20who%20had%20cited%20the%20sexual%20harassment%20allegations%20against%20him%20to%20hit%20out%20at%20him%20and%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-didigiri-bengal-governors-message-for-mamata-banerjee-5603072%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-didigiri-bengal-governors-message-for-mamata-banerjee-5603072%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-didigiri-bengal-governors-message-for-mamata-banerjee-5603072%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Argentina's%20Milei%20defends%20radical%20austerity%20plan%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715011891000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2FEAB6%2Fproduction%2F_133268006_18.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-latin-america-68935255%230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Argentine%20leader%20tells%20the%20BBC%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Bpolitical%20caste%26quot%3B%20is%20bearing%20the%20brunt%20of%20his%20reforms.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A34%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-latin-america-68935255%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-latin-america-68935255.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-latin-america-68935255.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Explained%3A%20Impact%20Of%20Heatwave%20On%20India's%20Election%20Season%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EHow%20will%20heat%20impact%20the%20biggest%20democratic%20exercise%20of%20the%20world%3F%20India%2C%20where%20parliamentary%20polls%20are%20underway%2C%20has%20been%20sweltering%20under%20unprecedented%20heatwaves%20ever%20since%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20summer%20season%20in%20April%2C%20and%20these%20are%20more%20pronounced%20in%20east%20and%20peninsular%20India%20than%20the%20north%20and%20northwest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%202024%20Indian%20general%20elections%202024%20are%20a%20two-and-a-half-month%20process%2C%20with%20voting%20taking%20place%20in%20seven%20phases%20till%20June%201%20where%20nearly%2097%20crore%20people%20are%20expected%20to%20exercise%20their%20voting%20rights.%20As%20elections%20enter%20the%20key%20phase%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%20May%2C%20the%20temperatures%20have%20also%20started%20peaking.%20Globally%20as%20well%2C%20each%20month%20is%20setting%20a%20new%20all-time%20record.%20The%20last%2010%20months%2C%20since%20June%202023%2C%20have%20been%20the%20hottest%20on%20record%2C%20mainly%20because%20of%20a%20super%20El%20Nino.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApril%202024%20also%20seems%20to%20be%20following%20similar%20temperature%20trends%20and%20will%20most%20likely%20be%20the%2011th%20hottest%20month%20in%20a%20row.%20Sheer%20temperature%20and%20humidity%20will%20increasingly%20make%20it%20harder%20to%20work%20in%20the%20open%20and%20India's%20ongoing%20election%20process%20has%20shown%20how%20much%20the%20complexities%20of%20weather%20and%20climate%20impact%20the%20voting%20and%20canvassing%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20led%20to%20an%20intense%20heatwave%20in%20India%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20India%20Meteorological%20Department%20(IMD)%20had%20already%20predicted%20more%20than%20double%20the%20average%20heatwaves%20during%20April-June%2C%20i.e.%2010%20to%2020%20days%20of%20heat%20waves%20against%20a%20normal%20of%20four%20to%20eight%20days%20to%20be%20precise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20heat%20this%20year%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20worse%20than%20in%202023%2C%20which%20has%20been%20the%20warmest%20year%20on%20record%20to%20date.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMercury%20has%20been%20settling%20between%2042%20and%2045%20degrees%2C%20even%20soaring%20to%2047%20degrees%20in%20some%20parts%20of%20the%20country.%20April%20has%20seen%20one%20of%20the%20longest%20spells%20of%20heatwave%20extending%20up%20to%2015%20days.%20Parts%20of%20east%20and%20peninsular%20India%20have%20been%20the%20worst%20hit%2C%20as%20they%20are%20also%20battling%20humidity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKerala%20is%20under%20the%20grip%20of%20a%20record%20heatwave%20and%20has%20reported%2010%20deaths%20due%20to%20heat%20stress%20while%20waiting%20in%20voting%20queues.%20According%20to%20the%20Kerala%20State%20Disaster%20Management%20Authority%20(KSDMA)%2C%20around%20413%20heat-related%20health%20issues%20like%20sunburn%2C%20rashes%2C%20and%20heat%20stroke%20cases%20have%20been%20reported%20until%20April%2022.%20Odisha%20has%20also%20recorded%20one%20death%20and%20around%20124%20have%20been%20hospitalised%20due%20to%20heat-related%20illnesses%20across%2016%20districts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaximum%20temperatures%20across%20India%20show%20large%20parts%20of%20the%20country%20as%20a%20large%20red%20mass%2C%20indicating%20above-normal%20day%20temperatures%20over%20most%20parts%20of%20the%20country.%20An%20unprecedented%20rise%20in%20temperatures%20can%20be%20attributed%20to%20the%20absence%20of%20pre-monsoon%20rain%20and%20thundershowers%20during%20April.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECountrywide%20cumulative%20rainfall%20was%20deficit%20to%20the%20tune%20of%2020%20per%20cent.%20Rainfall%20during%20April%20over%20south%20peninsular%20India%20(12.6%20mm)%20was%20the%20fifth%20lowest%20since%201901%20and%20the%20second%20lowest%20since%202001.%20This%20was%20followed%20by%20east%20and%20northeast%20India%20which%20was%20deficit%20by%2039%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Climate%20Central%2C%20a%20US-based%20organisation%20working%20on%20climate%20change%2C%20day%20temperatures%20were%20at%20least%20twice%20as%20likely%20because%20of%20climate%20change.%20The%20temperature%20conditions%20in%20the%20southern%20half%20of%20the%20country%20had%20a%20much%20stronger%20climate%20change%20influence.%20In%20coastal%20areas%2C%2037%20degrees%20Celsius%20is%20commonly%20used%20as%20a%20threshold%20for%20dangerous%20heat.%20This%20temperature%20occurred%20throughout%20most%20of%20the%20country%2C%20including%20along%20the%20eastern%20coast.%20Thirty-six%20out%20of%2051%20major%20cities%20had%20three%20or%20more%20days%20above%2037%20degrees%20since%20the%20start%20of%20the%20election%20season%20(April%2019-April%2030)%2C%20and%2018%20cities%20had%20more%20than%20three%20days%20above%2040%20degrees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPersistence%20of%20anticyclones%20over%20Oman%20and%20adjoining%20areas%20and%20over%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20did%20not%20let%20the%20formation%20of%20any%20weather%20systems.%20In%20wake%20of%20this%2C%20the%20sea%20breeze%20was%20cut%20off%20over%20Odisha%20and%20West%20Bengal%20for%20most%20days%2C%20paving%20the%20way%20for%20unabated%20hot%20winds%20from%20land%2C%20leading%20to%20soaring%20temperatures%2C%26quot%3B%20IMD%20Director%20General%20Mrityunjay%20Mohapatra%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20due%20to%20the%20passage%20of%20western%20disturbances%20at%20regular%20intervals%2C%20heatwaves%20did%20not%20set%20in%20over%20northwestern%20plains.%20In%20addition%20to%20this%2C%20remnants%20of%20receding%20El%20Nino%20have%20also%20contributed%20to%20the%20heat%20stress.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAshok%20Lavasa%2C%20former%20Election%20Commissioner%2C%20explains%20how%20India%20can%20adjust%20its%20election%20process%20to%20increasing%20summer%20heatwaves.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWeather%20conditions%20are%20always%20taken%20into%20account%20to%20avert%20major%20disruption.%20There%20are%20mitigation%20measures%20which%20are%20taken%20well%20beforehand%20like%20arrangements%20for%20making%20people%20stand%20in%20the%20queue%20in%20cool%20places%2C%20availability%20of%20drinking%20water%2C%20etc%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20provision%20by%20which%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20can%20conduct%20elections%20anytime%20in%20180%20days%20but%20they%20have%20to%20be%20extremely%20careful%20that%20the%20term%20of%20the%20government%20is%20not%20curtailed%20even%20by%20a%20day.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20problem%20is%20that%20the%20February-March%20period%20is%20exam%20time%20in%20schools%20and%20colleges%20so%20one%20cannot%20disrupt%20the%20academic%20cycle%20as%20well.%20%26quot%3BThe%20maximum%20precautions%20are%20taken%20to%20minimise%20the%20extremes.%20However%2C%20one%20may%20consider%20this%2C%20if%20(temperatures)%20continue%20to%20increase%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715011800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-04%2F5b19rr6o_heatwave-generic-reuters_625x300_18_April_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexplained-how-will-heatwave-impact-election-season-in-india-5603145%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%2C%20where%20parliamentary%20polls%20are%20underway%2C%20has%20been%20sweltering%20under%20unprecedented%20heatwaves%20ever%20since%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20summer%20season%20in%20April%2C%20and%20these%20are%20more%20pronounced%20in%20east%20and%20peninsular%20India%20than%20the%20north%20and%20northwest.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexplained-how-will-heatwave-impact-election-season-in-india-5603145%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexplained-how-will-heatwave-impact-election-season-in-india-5603145%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexplained-how-will-heatwave-impact-election-season-in-india-5603145%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Putin's%20fifth%20inauguration%20marks%20more%20of%20the%20same%20for%20a%20Russia%20with%20little%20choice%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715011140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F05%2F1920x1080%2Fskynews-russia-kremlin-politics_6545527.jpg%3F20240506172127%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fvladimir-putins-fifth-presidential-inauguration-marks-more-of-the-same-for-a-russia-with-little-choice-13130666%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20term%20%26quot%3Binauguration%26quot%3B%20may%20feel%20slightly%20misleading.%20After%20all%2C%20this%20is%20not%20his%20first%20time.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fvladimir-putins-fifth-presidential-inauguration-marks-more-of-the-same-for-a-russia-with-little-choice-13130666%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2