0overs%2C%20they've%20all%20been%20against%20pace.%20But%20Punjab's%20captain%20%5B%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Sam%20Curran%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F108668-sam-curran-playerprofile%5C%22%3ESam%20Curran%3C%2Fa%3E%5D%20played%20a%20master%20stroke.%20He%20employed%20a%20spinner%2C%26quot%3B%20Sidhu%20said%20on%20Star%20Sports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDhoni%20wasn't%20prepared.%20For%207-8%20months%2C%20he%20hasn't%20faced%20spin.%20It%20was%20almost%20as%20if%20he%20was%20startled.%20Tactic%20is%20like%20how%20you%20take%20the%20stinger%20out%20of%20the%20bee%20without%20getting%20stung.%20And%20that%20is%20where%20the%20game%20turned.%20And%20on%20top%20of%20it%2C%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Harpreet%20Brar%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F110975-harpreet-brar-playerprofile%5C%22%3EHarpreet%20Brar%3C%2Fa%3E%20bowled%20a%20faster%20one%20to%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Shivam%20Dube%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F107521-shivam-dubey-playerprofile%5C%22%3EShivam%20Dube%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Cannoned%20onto%20the%20stumps.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERegarding%20dismissing%20Dhoni%C2%A0%20on%20Sunday%2C%20Harshal%20said%3A%C2%A0%26quot%3BWicket%20was%20on%20drier%20side.%20I%20have%20too%20much%20respect%20for%20him%20to%20celebrate%20when%20I%20get%20him%20out%20(on%20Dhoni).%20One%20of%20the%20advantages%20of%20playing%20a%20day%20game%20is%20that%20the%20square%20is%20quite%20rough.%20So%20the%20ball%20starts%20reversing.%20In%20my%20first%20over%20it%20was%20reversing.%20It's%20all%20about%20the%20feel%20of%20that%20delivery%20(slower%20one).%20More%20you%20bowl%20the%20better%20you%20get.%20Most%20batters%20don't%20pick%20it.%20Have%20been%20practicing%20in%20the%20nets%2C%20and%20when%20it%20comes%20out%20it%20gives%20you%20great%20results%2C%26quot%3B%20Harshal%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715009460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fcoh2s94o_dhoni-bowled_625x300_06_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Fms-dhonis-own-medicine-used-to-fool-him-on-csk-greats-struggles-ex-india-stars-blunt-take-5602961%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22For%20two%20successive%20matches%20now%2C%20MS%20Dhoni%20has%20been%20dismissed%20in%20the%20IPL%202024%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BPlease%20Be%20Part%20Of%20Our%20Tourism%26quot%3B%3A%20Maldives%20Urges%20India%20Amid%20Strained%20Ties%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20number%20of%20Indian%20tourists%20visiting%20the%20Maldives%20dwindling%20amidst%20strained%20bilateral%20ties%2C%20the%20archipelago%20nation's%20tourism%20minister%20on%20Monday%20urged%20Indians%20to%20contribute%20to%20the%20country's%20economy%20which%20is%20dependent%20on%20tourism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20with%20PTI%20Videos%20here%2C%20Maldivian%20Tourism%20Minister%20Ibrahim%20Faisal%20emphasised%20on%20the%20historical%20relations%20between%20his%20country%20and%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20a%20history.%20Our%20newly%20elected%20government%20also%20wants%20to%20work%20together%20(with%20India).%20We%20always%20promote%20peace%20and%20a%20friendly%20environment.%20Our%20people%20and%20the%20government%20will%20give%20a%20warm%20welcome%20to%20Indian%20arrivals.%20As%20the%20Tourism%20Minister%2C%20I%20want%20to%20tell%20Indians%20to%20please%20be%20a%20part%20of%20Maldives'%20tourism.%20Our%20economy%20depends%20on%20tourism%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20full-blown%20backlash%20was%20directed%20at%20the%20Maldives%20following%20derogatory%20remarks%20against%20India%20and%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20on%20social%20media%20by%20three%20Maldivian%20officials%20after%20Modi%20posted%20photos%20and%20video%20of%20the%20pristine%20Lakshadweep%20Islands%20on%20India's%20west%20coast%20on%20January%206%20on%20his%20X%20handle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EScores%20of%20Indians%2C%20including%20multiple%20celebrities%2C%20cancelled%20their%20reservations%20and%20dropped%20plans%20to%20visit%20Maldives.%20The%20tourism%20arrival%20statistics%20reflected%20how%20from%20being%20a%20top%20visitor%20country%2C%20India's%20position%20went%20down%20from%20topmost%20to%20sixth%20position%20after%20January.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20sun.mv%20report%20published%20on%20Monday%2C%20the%20number%20of%20tourist%20arrivals%20from%20India%20declined%20by%2042%20per%20cent%20in%20the%20first%20four%20months%20of%20this%20year%20compared%20to%20the%20first%20four%20months%20of%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20start%20of%20this%20year%2C%20India%20was%20the%20top%20tourist%20market%20for%20the%20Maldives.%20Shortly%20into%20the%20year%2C%20India%20dropped%20to%20sixth%20place%20amongst%20the%20top%20tourist%20markets%2C%20the%20news%20portal%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Tourism%20Ministry%20statistics%2C%20Maldives%20recorded%20a%20total%20of%2043%2C991%20tourist%20arrivals%20from%20India%20as%20of%20May%204.%20Between%20January%20and%20April%20of%20last%20year%2C%20Maldives%20recorded%2073%2C785%20tourist%20arrivals.%20This%20year%2C%20the%20number%20stands%20at%2042%2C638.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20attributed%20the%20steep%20decline%20in%20Indian%20tourists%20to%20the%20strained%20relations%20between%20India%20and%20the%20Maldives%20after%20the%20new%20administration%20led%20by%20President%20Mohamed%20Muizzu%20assumed%20office%20in%20November%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20India-Maldives%20ties%20have%20come%20under%20stress%20as%20President%20Muizzu%2C%20widely%20seen%20as%20a%20pro-China%20leader%2C%20maintained%20after%20assuming%20charge%20as%20the%20president%20in%20November%20that%20he%20will%20keep%20his%20election%20promise%20of%20evicting%20Indian%20military%20personnel%20from%20his%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20coming%20to%20power%2C%20Muizzu%20forced%20the%20withdrawal%20of%20the%2088%20Indian%20military%20personnel%20manning%20three%20aviation%20platforms%20gifted%20by%20India%20to%20the%20Maldives.%20He%20has%20previously%20accused%20India%20of%20meddling%20in%20the%20affairs%20of%20the%20Maldives%20and%20won%20the%20presidential%20elections%20in%20September%20last%20year%20with%20an%20%26quot%3BIndia%20Out%26quot%3B%20campaign.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Maldives%20is%20India's%20key%20maritime%20neighbour%20in%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%20Region%20(IOR)%20and%20occupies%20a%20special%20place%20in%20its%20initiatives%20like%20'SAGAR'%20(Security%20and%20Growth%20for%20All%20in%20the%20Region)%20and%20the%20'Neighbourhood%20First%20Policy'%20of%20the%20Modi%20government%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715009100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fo7415eug_maldives-generic-facebook_625x300_09_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fplease-be-part-of-our-tourism-maldives-urges-india-amid-strained-ties-5602280%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22With%20the%20number%20of%20Indian%20tourists%20visiting%20the%20Maldives%20dwindling%20amidst%20strained%20bilateral%20ties%2C%20the%20archipelago%20nation's%20tourism%20minister%20on%20Monday%20urged%20Indians%20to%20contribute%20to%20the%20country's%20economy%20which%20is%20dependent%20on%20tourism.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fplease-be-part-of-our-tourism-maldives-urges-india-amid-strained-ties-5602280%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fplease-be-pa