%20store%20room%2C%20and%20an%20oxygen%20cylinder%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-22-at-12.06.24-PM-1714725063.jpeg%201280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-22-at-12.06.24-PM-1714725063-300x169.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-22-at-12.06.24-PM-1714725063-500x282.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-22-at-12.06.24-PM-1714725063-768x433.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-22-at-12.06.24-PM-1714725063-150x85.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-348889%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22722%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EEach%20boat%20comprises%20two%20medical%20beds%2C%20a%20mobile%20X-ray%2C%20a%20small%20pathological%20unit%2C%20a%20medical%20store%20room%2C%20and%20an%20oxygen%20cylinder%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Wohab%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20pregnancy%20cases%20top%20the%20charts%2C%20the%20other%20cases%20include%20young%20couples%20wishing%20to%20begin%20their%20family%20planning%2C%20women%20seeking%20help%20with%20oral%20contraceptives%2C%20patients%20who%20need%20stitches%20and%20dressing%20for%20their%20injuries%2C%20and%20those%20who%20need%20antibiotics.%20Running%20a%20clinic%20set%20up%20in%20the%20constricted%20space%20of%20a%20boat%20is%20not%20ideal%2C%20but%20the%20terrain%20makes%20it%20the%20only%20option%20feasible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEach%20boat%20clinic%20includes%20two%20medical%20beds%2C%20a%20mobile%20X-ray%2C%20a%20small%20pathological%20unit%2C%20a%20medical%20store%20room%2C%20and%20an%20oxygen%20cylinder.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20its%20inception%2C%20eight%20lakh%20patients%20have%20been%20helped%20by%20%3Ca%20rel%