%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fshis-1714725744-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fshis-1714725744-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fshis-1714725744-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fshis-1714725744-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-348892%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EEye%20checkup%20camps%20are%20conducted%20to%20detect%20glaucoma%2C%20disturbances%20in%20vision%20and%20other%20ocular%20problems%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Wohab%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20this%2C%20the%20foundation%20has%20helped%20rehabilitate%2044%20dacoits%20and%20thieves%2C%20and%20engage%20them%20in%20skill%20development.%20In%20an%20attempt%20to%20restore%20women%E2%80%99s%20sense%20of%20agency%2C%20they%20have%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F345161%2Ftvaran-by-cisco-villgro-empower-women-led-startups-female-entrepreneurs-climate-action%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esecured%20loans%20for%20women%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20wish%20to%20start%20a%20self-help%20group%20and%20earn%20a%20living.%20Their%20initiative%20for%20deaf%20and%20mute%20children%20encourages%20them%20to%20study%2C%20and%20some%20of%20them%20have%20even%20graduated%2C%20says%20Wohab.%20They%20also%20have%20a%20centre%20where%20girls%20are%20taught%20and%20helped%20to%20complete%20their%20school%20and%20college%20education.%20%E2%80%9COver%20700%20children%20have%20been%20helped%20in%20total%20and%20many%20of%20them%20have%20secured%20Government%20jobs%2C%E2%80%9D%20Wohab%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20educational%20endeavours%20are%20based%20on%20the%20belief%20that%20the%20youth%20of%20the%20Sundarbans%20are%20bubbling%20with%20creativity%20that%20mustn%E2%80%99t%20be%20stifled.%20These%20programmes%20are%20a%20step%20towards%20helping%20these%20children%20to%20channel%20their%20talents%20in%20a%20constructive%20direction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEach%20time%20the%20couple%20has%20encountered%20adversity%20%E2%80%94%20sometimes%20with%20diminishing%20funds%2C%20other%20times%20with%20the%20climate%20playing%20spoilsport%20%E2%80%94%20they%20are%20reminded%20of%20why%20they%20started.%20From%20a%20humble%20initiative%20in%20a%20tea%20shop%2C%20the%20foundation%20has%20evolved%20into%20a%20place%20where%20new%20possibilities%20are%20given%20space%20to%20grow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EIf%20you%E2%80%99d%20like%20to%20support%20them%20with%20funds%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.shisindia.org%2Fsupportus%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ehere%E2%80%99s%20a%20link%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20with%20the%20details.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715003816000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-22-at-10.31.59-AM-1714724688.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D348884%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20SHIS%20Foundation%2C%20founded%20by%20Mohammed%20Abdul%20Wohab%20and%20Sabitri%20Pal%2C%20operates%20in%20the%20Sundarbans%2C%20West%20Bengal.%20They%20provide%20essential%20healthcare%20services%20in%20the%20area%20through%20many%20initiatives%20like%20boat%20clinics%2C%20tuberculosis%20control%20programmes%2C%20etc.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F348884%2Fsenior-citizens-healthcare-boat-clinic-in-sundarbans-shis-foundation-abdul-wohab-sabitri-pal%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2