-home-garden-make-pesticide-insecticide-spray-organic-gardener-brahmadev-kumar%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Heatwave%20Alerts%20in%20India%3A%20How%20to%20Design%20Homes%20that%20Don%E2%80%99t%20Need%20ACs%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20unbearable%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Vinaya%20K%2C%20a%20Bengaluru%20resident%2C%20highlighting%20how%20the%20incessant%20heat%20has%20disrupted%20her%20daily%20life.%20Despite%20experiencing%20a%20day%20of%20relief%20with%20some%20rain%2C%20the%20city%20is%20still%20facing%20a%20dry%20spell%20of%20over%20150%20days%2C%20and%20the%20heat%20continues%20to%20prevail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Meteorological%20Department%20describes%20heat%20waves%20as%20occurring%20when%20the%20maximum%20temperature%20in%20plains%20reaches%20at%20least%2040%20degrees%20Celsius%20or%20more%2C%20and%20at%20least%2030%20degrees%20Celsius%20or%20more%20in%20hilly%20regions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20department%20has%20issued%20a%20warning%20for%20hotter%20temperatures%20across%20several%20states%20in%20the%20coming%20weeks.%20According%20to%20a%20report%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Times%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20temperatures%20have%20soared%20between%2040%20to%2045%20degrees%20Celsius%20in%20parts%20of%20Odisha%20earlier%20this%20week.%20Similar%20conditions%20have%20been%20observed%20in%20Gangetic%20West%20Bengal%2C%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Jharkhand%2C%20Vidarbha%2C%20and%20southwestern%20parts%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20among%20other%20regions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERising%20temperatures%20lead%20to%20an%20increase%20in%20the%20use%20of%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F281434%2Fagra-data-scientist-builds-solar-power-eco-friendly-air-conditioner-exalta%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20air%20conditioners%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20electricity%20as%20people%20try%20to%20escape%20the%20heat.%20%E2%80%9CWorking%20fro