F330088%2Fkerala-architect-designer-anupa-kurian-renovates-century-old-ancestral-home-sustainable-upcycle%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehe%20house%20breathable%20and%20cooler%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20summer.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20always%20a%20good%20idea%20to%20look%20back%20at%20our%20ancestors%20and%20how%20they%20used%20various%20techniques%20to%20deal%20with%20indoor%20heat.%20Evaporative%20cooling%20is%20a%20technique%20where%20you%20build%20an%20indoor%20water%20body%2C%20let%E2%80%99s%20say%20a%20fountain%20to%20cool%20down%20the%20temperature%20inside%20the%20house%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20water%20body%20in%20the%20house%20can%20do%20wonders.%20Additionally%2C%20it%20can%20also%20cool%20down%20the%20air%20that%20passes%20through%20the%20home.%20This%20method%20is%20very%20effective%20in%20homes%20in%20the%20northern%20parts%20of%20the%20country%20where%20the%20humidity%20is%20relatively%20low%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETrees%20and%20shade%20keep%20your%20home%20happy%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrees%20have%20been%20the%20best%20friends%20of%20humans%20since%20the%20beginning%20of%20time.%20From%20giving%20us%20food%20to%20shelter%20under%20its%20shade%2C%20trees%20are%20something%20that%20the%20architects%20advise%20to%20have%20around%20the%20home.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20cannot%20emphasise%20enough%20the%20need%20and%20importance%20of%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F348074%2Fsustainable-home-wayanad-kerala-george-ramapuram-earthitects-hillside-jungle-home-nature%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20trees%20around%20your%20home%3C%2Fa%3E.%20They%20bring%20in%20shade%2C%20and%20wind%20and%20moderate%20the%20temperature%20around%20them.%20Plant%20as%20many%20trees%20as%20you%20can%20around%20your%20home%20and%20try%20to%20incorporate%20the%20existing%20ones%20in%20the%20design.%20Trust%20me%2C%20they%20are%20going%20to%20be%20a%20lifesaver%20in%20the%20heat%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20George%20Ramapuran%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20sustainable%20design%20firm%2C%20Eartitects.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20built%20numerous%20estates%20around%20the%20theme%20of%20sustainability%20and%20nature%20conservation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAgreeing%20with%20George%2C%20Shipra%20also%20emphasises%20the%20importance%20of%20greenery%20to%20keep%20the%20heat%20at%20bay.%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20constructing%20the%20home%2C%20you%20can%20always%20look%20at%20the%20region-specific%20trees%20and%20plant%20them%20in%20the%20areas%20where%20your%20home%20will%20have%20verandas%20and%20windows.%20This%20will%20ensure%20shade%20in%20those%20areas%20and%20also%20will%20help%20in%20better%20wind%20circulation%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20840px)%20100vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fveedu-1-1-1-1694786484.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Architects%20suggest%20planting%20trees%20around%20the%20house%20to%20increase%20shade%20and%20reduce%20temperatures.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fveedu-1-1-1-1694786484.jpg%20840w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fveedu-1-1-1-1694786484-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fveedu-1-1-1-1694786484-500x261.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fveedu-1-1-1-1694786484-768x401.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fveedu-1-1-1-1694786484-150x78.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-330098%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22439%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcapti